info: Uttarakhand State Road Investment Program -Project 2 will help the State of Uttarakhand to (i) improve a sub-network of roads totaling about 898 kilometers; (ii) undertake business process re-engineering of Public Works Department (PWD); and (iii) increase PWD staff's asset management skills.
name: MFF-UTTARAKHAND STATE ROAD INVESTMENT PROGRAM-PROJECT 2
